FBIS4-67829 "jptnd010___94074" JPRS-TND-94-010 JPRS PROLIFERATION ISSUES 15 April 1994 CENTRAL EURASIA UKRAINE Expelled Swede Sought To Obtain Nuclear Warhead Components Expelled Swede Sought To Obtain Nuclear Warhead Components LD1604082694 Kiev UNIAN in Ukrainian 2005 GMT 15 Apr 94 LD1604082694 Kiev UNIAN Ukrainian BFN [Text] On 15 April the press center of the Security Service of Ukraine reported that Swedish subject Erik Olaf Estenson, born in 1962, who was temporarily staying on the territory of our state, was expelled from Ukraine for attempts to carry out actions which can be qualified as international nuclear terrorism in relation to a foreign state. As UNIAN learned from reliable sources, the Swedish subject was seeking contacts with relevant specialists with the aim of taking nuclear warhead components away from Ukraine. According to unofficial data, the organization which, presumably, tasked Estensson has not yet been disclosed.
